data.description: Welcome to this partially renovated lovely rancher in the desirable neighborhood of Hamiltowne. This bright and spacious 4 bed 2 bathroom rancher is located in a quiet cul de sac with a fenced in huge backyard.   Walk up the front porch and you'll find a tidy area to overlook the neighborhood . Beautiful brick front with large bay window bringing in tons of natural light that beams off the lovely floors with open living area and eat-in an updated kitchen with updated counters/backsplash and appliances. 2 large bedrooms with ample closet space and 1 updated bath on the main level. The lower level has two large bedrooms and a full bath and tons of storage space and washroom.  The backyard is one of the focal points for some- great space for kids/friends/ family/ animals to play and entertain. so much potential.  The owners were going to complete more renovations but are not able due to lack of time,,, and are leaving the materials behind for future owner. The home is being sold as-is. Come check it out!
